window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>PROTECT - DEVELOP - BUILD</b></p> <p>It has been a year and a half of living with the System. Jason and his friends are not just surviving, but are preparing for the future. Thanks to a new quest, they are establishing a kingdom in the former southwest portion of the United States. They are trying to protect humanity wherever possible and build a kingdom to defend their part of the world.</p> <p>They are helping others build secure settlements and become self-sufficient. At the same time, the team is finding and cleaning up the messes the elves created before they were defeated and exiled.</p> <p>Thrust into a leadership role they were not looking for, Jason and his friends find a way to pass on what they have learned while keeping humanity ahead of the threats around every corner.</p> <p>Jason and his friends are building a future for their friends and family. To do that, they must clear dungeons, rebuild settlements, and support new and old allies in book four of this LitRPG series.</p>"; 
